OOC: This is more than just a Halloween ripoff, believe me.

????????::

The plant-creature stops his odd dance and looks at Destructor and 
Proto.  "Heehee, I forgot to introduce myself, how rude ... PUMPSKIN, 
TERRORIZE!"

The central jack-o-lantern and four of the tentacles buckle and fold 
into a greenish body, arms, and legs.  The other four tentacles 
remain on his back, and a head which looks like a smaller jack-o-
lantern tops it all off.  The small Maximal insignia belies the fact 
that Pumpskin honestly thinks he's a Predacon.
